node.text:
We need your help!
We've just released our newest design on our website, but are having some trouble coming up with a name for it. We need something that really captures the nature of this page, and also fits this design. Here's where you can come in! We need you to come up with, and submit names for this design in the comments. We'll pick the one we like the best, change its name to that, and send you a shirt for free!

Here's how to submit an entry:
1. Like this post
2. Comment the name of the design
3. Tag a friend in the same comment

Feel free to submit multiple entries, but you have to tag a different person each time or it won't count! May the best name win!

Submissions will be closed on Friday, July 30th at 11:59 PM ET, and a winner will be announced the following day.
